<h2>What You Should Do Today</h2>

<p>If your business has a website, here is a quick checklist:</p>

<ol>
  <li>Check if you have a privacy policy. If not, you are already non-compliant.</li>
  <li>Check if your site uses HTTPS. If the URL starts with http:// (no "s"), fix this immediately.</li>
  <li>Check your cookie consent. Does your site set tracking cookies before the user agrees? That is a violation.</li>
  <li>Review who has access to your customer data. Limit it to people who actually need it.</li>
  <li>If you process data from 200+ people, register with the NDPC.</li>
</ol>

